<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حجة) <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(أو عليَّ حجة (للَّه)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> أو) <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(علي نذر؛ أو عليَّ)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> نذر للَّه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
